<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/123710279-aurora"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1626826705i/123710279._UY100_CR5,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
